msgid "Return to The Devourer Below"
msgstr "重返地底噬魔"

msgid "Scenario III: Return to The Devourer Below"
msgstr "冒险III：重返地底噬魔"

msgid "Put the Main Path location into play. Shuffle the 10 copies of Arkham Woods, choose 4 of them at random, and put them into play without looking at their revealed sides. Remove the other 6 from the game. Each investigator begins play at the Main Path."
msgstr "将主道路放置入场。将10张阿卡姆密林混洗，随机抽出4张放置入场，请不要查看已揭示面。然后将另外6张移出游戏。每位调查员从主道路开始游戏。"

msgid "Set the Ritual Site and Umôrdhoth cards aside, out of play. Flip over the \"Return to The Devourer Below\" scenario card and attach it to Umôrdhoth"
msgstr "将仪式场所地点和乌默尔多斯敌人放在一边，位于场外。将“重返地底噬魔”冒险卡翻面并叠加到乌默尔多斯。"
